summary:
Greenland 'artist' Malik Chemnitz is tracing J. Scott Campbell's art!
He's made posters of them and selling them for...
body:
Greenland ‘artist’ Malik Chemnitz is tracing J. Scott Campbell’s art!

He’s made posters of them and selling them for money.

People that do not know or care that Malik have traced them buy them from FaceBook.

Some do not care at all that they are traced, calling Malik a great artist. Which is sending bad message for future Greenland artists!

People have them hanging on their wall at home, even Café Pascucci have one that is not included in the image.

Malik do not care at all, he said that it was because of him that 98% people from Greenland began to know about J. Scott Campbell, which is not true.

I want this spread, I want this to go viral because Malik said that he have no shame and won’t apologize for tracing J. Scott Campbell’s artworks!

EDIT:

I also want to point it out that he Googled the images and traced over them then included Greenlandic motives.

He have also copied others artworks like Natascha Pedersen Makeup (look up at her FaceBook)

She made a post about him.

summary: “We’re the Avengers. We can bust up arms dealers all the livelong day, but that up there, that’s the Endgame. How were YOU guys...
body:
“We’re the Avengers. We can bust up arms dealers all the livelong day, but that up there, that’s the Endgame. How were YOU guys planning on beating that?”

“…Together.”

“HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!!!”

“That’s a fake laugh!”

“It’s real! It’s the most real, authentic, hysterical laugh of my entire life because THAT is not a plan!” 

“It’s barely a concept.”
